<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><note n="437-1">This inscription is a Telugu version of A.R. No. 317 of 1896, sun are engraved at the end.</note>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>śakavarṣaṁbulu 1373 Agunēṁṭṭi prajāpa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ticaṁvvacara maga śuklapaṁcami gūruvārananu
<lb n="3"/>kaḷiṁgaparikṣalu hēmakarāpātruṁḍunu ravidā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>sapaṭānāyuṁḍunu Iddaṟunnu śrīkūrmanāthadē
<lb n="5" break="no"/>varaku yiruvaIĒnupūṭlu kṣētramu bhaṁḍara
<lb n="6" break="no"/>na kalaṁpi grāmanaku nunyaviḍiciri <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattaṁ
<lb n="7"/>vā paradattaṁ vā yō harēta vasuṁdharā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> ṣaṣṭi
<lb n="8" break="no"/>rvaruṣasa<supplied reason="omitted">ha</supplied> śraṇi viṣṭāyāṁ jāyatē krimi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

